 \mbox{sgn}(\xi_{i}):=\begin{cases} -1 & \text{if } \xi_{i} < 0, \\ 0 & \text{if } \xi_{i} = 0, \\ 1 & \text{if } \xi_{i} > 0. \end{cases} 
